hadiths[54]{hadithnumber,text}:
689,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney (is gharz sey) masjid banai ke is mein Allah Taala ka zikr kiya jaey, Allah jannat mein us ka ghar banaeyga."
690,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye qiyamat ki nishani hai ke log masaajid main eik dusrey par fakhr kerengey."
691,"Hazrat Ibrahim sey riwayat hai ke main gali mein apney walid mohtaram par Quran Majeed ki qirat kar raha tha, jab mainey sajdey ki aayat padhi to aap ney wahin sajda kar diya. mainey kaha : abba jaan ! aap raastey mein sajda kar rahey hain? farmaney lagey : mainey Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna, wo farmatey they : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : kon si masjid sab sey pehley banai qaee? aap ney farmaya : Masjide-Haram (Baitullah). mainey kaha : phir kon si? aap ney farmaya : Masjide-Aqsaa (Baitul-maqdis). mainey kaha : unkey darmiyan kitna fasla hai? aap ney farmaya : chaalis saal wesey sari zamin terey liye namaz ki jagah hai, jahan bhi terey liye namaz ka waqt ho jaey, namaz padh ley."
692,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna ke jo shakhs is (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki) masjid mein namaz padhey to Masjide-Nabwi ki namaz dusri masaajid ki hazar namaz sey afzal hai, magar Masjide-Kaaba mein namaz (Masjide-Nabwi sey bhi afzal hai)."
693,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam), Usama bin Zaid, Bilal aur Usman bin Talha Baitullah mein dakhil huye aur unhoney darwaza band kar liya (taake log bheed na keren). phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney darwaza khola to main sab sey pehley dakhil huwa. main Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila. mainey un sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Kaabey mein namaz padhi hai? unhoney kaha : han, aap ney (agli saf key baain taraf waley) do Yamni sutonon key darmiyan namaz padhi hai."
694,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud Alaihimussalam ney jab Baitul-maqdis banaya to Allah Taala sey teen khasusiyat maangin : aisa faisla jo Allah Taala key hukm key muwaafiq ho. ye maan li gaee. aisi hukumat jo unkey baad kisi key laaiq na ho. ye bhi maan li gaee. jab aap masjid (Baitul-maqdis) bananey sey farigh huye to ye dua maangi ke jo shakhs bhi is masjid mein aaye aur usey aaney par namaz hi ney ubhaaraa ho to usey gunahon sey is tarah saaf kar dey jis tarah uski maa ney usey (gunahon sey paak) janaa tha."
695,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key do shagrid Hazrat Abu-Salma aur Abu Abdullah Agharr bayan kartey hain ke hamney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey huye suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki masjid main eik namaz padhna dusri masaajid mein hazar namaz padhney sey afzal hai magar Masjide-Haram mein (Masjide-Nabwi sey bhi afzal hai) kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aakhiri Nabi hain aur aap ki masjid aakhiri masjid hai. Abu-Salma aur Abu Abdullah ney kaha : is mein hamein koi shak nahin tha ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees hi bayan kar rahey hain. is yaqin ney hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey is ki tehqiq karney sey rokey rakha yahan tak ke jab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to hamney is baat ka tazkira kiya aur eik doosrey ko malamat ki ke kyon na hamney is barey mein un sey tehqiq ki? yahan tak ke wo sarahat ke sath is hadees ko agar unhoney isey aap sey suna tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansub kar detey. hamari yehi haalat thi ke hamein Hazrat Abdullah bin Ibrahim bin Qaariz key sath majlis ka ittifaq huwa. hamney unkey samney ye hadees aur is barey mein hum sey honey wali kotahi ka zikr kiya to Abdullah bin Ibrahim hamein kehney lagey, meiain gawahi deta hun ke mainey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey suna hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main aakhiri Nabi hun aur meri masjid (kisi Nabi ki) aakhiri masjid hai."
696,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey ghar aur merey member ka darmiyani fasla jannat key baaghichon mein sey eik baaghichaa hai."
697,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey is member key paey jannat mein gadey huye hain."
698,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ka is masjid key barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya jiski buniyad shuru din sey taqwe par rakhi gaee hai. eik shakhs ney kaha : wo Masjide -Qubaa hai. doosrey ney kaha : wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki masjid hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo meri masjid (Masjide-Nabwi) hai.
699,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu Anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kabhi pedal aur kabhi sawar Masjide-Qubaa mein tashrif ley jaya kartey they.
700,"Hazrat Sahal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi (ghar sey) nikla yahan tak ke us masjid yani Masjide-Qubaa mein aaya aur is mein namaz padhi to usey eik Umrey key barabar sawab milega."
701,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen masjidon key ilawa kisi jagah ki taraf door-daraz sey sawariyan kas key na jaya jaey.(aur wo teen masjiden ye hain) : Masjide-Haram, Masjide-Nabwi aur Masjide-Aqsaa."
702,"Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum apni qom key wafad key taur par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye. hamney aap ki baiat ki aur aap key sath namazein padhein aur hamney aap ko bataya ke hamarey ilaqey mein hamara eik Girjaa hai aur hamney aap sey aap key wuzu sey bacha huwa pani manga. aap ney pani mangwaya, phir wuzu kiya aur kulli ki, phir us (pani) ko eik chhaagal mein undel diya aur farmaya : jaao jab tum apney ilaqey mein pahuncho to apney girjey ko tod dena aur uski jagah ye pani chhidak dena aur us jagah ko masjid bana lena. hamney kaha ke hamara ilaaqa bahut door hai aur garmi sakht hai. ye pani (wahan pahunchtey pahunchtey) khushk ho jaeyga. aap ney farmaya : is mein aur pani mila liya karna, bilashuba is sey is ki pakizgi hi mein izafa hoga. hum wapis chaley yahan tak ke jab apney ilaqey mein pahunchey to hamney apna girjaa tod diya, phir uski jagah wo mubarak pani chhidkaa aur us jagah masjid bana li, phir hamney is mein Azan kahi. is girjey mein qabila banu-Tey ka eik aadmi raahib (key taur par rehta) tha. jab us ney Azan suni to kehney laga : ye sachchi dawat hai, phir wo eik tiley ki taraf gaya aur uskey baad hamein nazar na aaya."
703,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo farmatey hain : jab Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to aap Madina Munawra key eik kinarey (Qubaa mein) eik qabiley mein utrey jinhein banu Amr bin Auf kaha jata tha. aap un mein chaudah raaten thehrey phir aap ney banu-Najjaar key sardaron ki taraf pegham bheja. wo talwaarein latkaaey huye aaye. aisey mehsus hota hai ke main ab bhi dekh raha hun Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni oontni par hain, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap key peechhey bethey hain aur banu-Najjaar key sardar aap key ird-gird hain yahan tak ke aap ney Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar key samney padaaw dala. (shuru shuru mein) aap ko jahan namaz ka waqt ho jata tha, namaz padh letey they. aap bakriyon key baadon mein bhi namaz padhtey rahey, phir aap ko masjid bananey ka hukm diya gaya to aap ney banu-Najjaar key sardaron ko bula bheja. wo aaye to aap ney farmaya : aey banu-Najjaar ! mujh sey apney is ehatey ka bhaaw (qeemat) karo. unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! hum to is ki qeemat sirf Allah Taala sey lein-gey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke us ehatey mein mushrikon ki qabren thin, kuchh weeraana (khandar) tha aur khajuron key darkht they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya to mushrikon ki qabren ukhed di gaeen darkht kaat diye gaey aur weeraaney humwaar kar diye gaey. unhoney masjid key qibley wali janib khajoor key darakhton ki line laga di aur pattharon ki chaukhat banai. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhu patthar uthatey they aur rajz (she'r) padhtey they. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi unkey sath they. wo (sab) kehtey they : aey Allah ! aakhirat ki khair key siwa koi khair nahin. Ansaar aur muhajrin ki madad farma."
704,"Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain jab Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ka waqt qarib huwa to aap apni chadar kabhi chehre anwar par dal letey, phir jab ghabrahat hoti to usey chehrey sey hata letey. isi haalat mein aap ney farmaya : Allah ki lanat ho yahudiyon aur esaiyon par jinhoney apney Anbiya ki qabron ko masjiden bana liya."
705,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Umme-Habiba aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney eik girjey ka zikr kiya jisey unhoney Habsha mein (hijrate-habsha key daur mein) dekha tha. is mein taswiren thin to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : un (esaiyon) ki ye aadat thi ke jab un mein koi nek aadmi faut ho jata to uski qabr par masjid bana detey aur is mein ye taswiren bana detey. qiyamat key din Allah Taala key nazdik ye tamam makhluq mein sey bad-tareen hongey.
706,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi jab apney ghar sey masjid key liye nikalta hai aur qadam uthata hai to (har qadam key liye) eik paaun uthaney par neki likhi jati hai aur doosra paaun uthaney par eik burai mitaai jati hai."
707,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ki aurat masjid mein janey ki ijazat talab karey to wo usey na rokey."
708,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi ye paudhaa (Ataa ney) pehley din (hadees bayan kartey huye) kaha : lahsun phir (doosrey moqey par) kaha : lahsun aur piyaz aur gandanaa (piyaazi) khaye to wo hamari masjidon key qarib na aaye kyonkey farishton ko us chiz sey takleef hoti hai jis sey insan takleef mehsus kartey hain."
709,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke aey logo ! tum un do badboodaar paudhon ko khatey ho, yani lahsun aur piyaz halanke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap kisi aadmi sey un ki boo paatey to uskey barey mein aap hukm farmatey aur usey Baqee (Masjide-Nabwi sey muttasil (lage hue) qabristaan) ki taraf nikal diya jata, lihaza jisney unhein khana hi ho, wo unhein pakka kar un ki boo khatam kar ley."
710,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab aetikaf ka irada farmatey to subah ki namaz padh kar aetikaf wali jagah mein dakhil hotey. eik dafa aap ney ramzanul mubarak key aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf ka irada farmaya, chunanche aap ney hukm diya aur aap key liye (masjid mein) eik khema lagaya gaya. Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney hukm diya to unka khema bhi laga diya gaya. jab Hazrat Zainab (Raziallahu anha) ney unka khema laga dekha to unhoney bhi khema lagwaa liya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye sab kuchh dekha to farmaya : kya ye neki ka irada rakhti hain? (yani nahin rakhteen) phir (narazi ki bina par) aap ney us saal Ramzan mein aetikaf na kiya balke shawwaal key das din aetikaf kiya."
711,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) jange-khandaq key din zakhmi ho gaey. eik quraishi aadmi (Hibbaan bin Arqaa) ney unkey bazu ki badi rag mein teer maara. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey liye masjid mein khema laga diya taake aap qarib sey un ki iyaadat kar liya karen.
712,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum eik dafa masjid mein bethey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (apni nawaasi) Amaama binte Abul-Aas bin Rabeea ko uthaey huye hamarey paas aaye. wo abhi bachchi thi. un ki walida Zainab binte Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) thin. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz padhaai jab ke wo bachchi aap key kandhey par thi. aap jab rukoo farmatey to bachchi ko utaar detey aur jab khadey hotey to usey dobara utha letey yahan tak ke aap ney isi tarah namaz mukammal ki.
713,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik ghud-sawar dasta Najad ki taraf bheja. wo qabila banu Haneefa key eik aadmi ko jin ka naam Samaama bin Assaal tha, pakad kar laye. ye Yamaama walon key sardar they. aap ney unhein masjid key eik sutoon key sath baandh diya. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
714,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajjatul-wadaa mein oont par sawar ho kar tawaf kiya. aap Hajare-Aswad ko chhadi sey chhotey they.
715,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) neyJumaa mubarak key din namaze Juma sey qabl halqey bananey aur masjid mein kharid aur farokht karney sey mana farmaya hai.
716,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney masjid mein ashaar padhney sey mana farmaya hai.
717,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyeb sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Hassan bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) key paas sey guzrey jab ke wo masjid mein she'r padh rahey they. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein ghoor kar dekha to wo kehney lagey : mainey us waqt bhi (masjid mein) she'r padhey hain jab is mein aap sey behtar shakhsiyat mojud thi, (yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) phir wo (Hassan (Raziallahu anhu)) Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur kaha : kya aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna hai : (aey Hassan !) meri taraf sey (kafiron ko) jawab do. aey Allah ! uski rooh al-Qudus sey taeed farma. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! haan."
718,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik aadmi aaya aur masjid mein gum shuda janwer ka aelan karney laga chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah karey tujhey na miley.
719,Sufiyan kehtey hain ke mainey Amr sey puchha : kya aap ney Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey suna hai ke eik aadmi apney teer ley kar masjid sey guzra to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : un ki nokon ko haath mein pakad lo. us ney kaha : ji haan.
720,Hazrat Aswad sey riwayat hai ke main aur Alqama Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key yahaan gaey. aap ney hum sey puchha : un logon ney namaz padh li hai? hamney kaha : nahin. farmaya : utho aur namaz padho. hum aap key peechhey khadey honey lagey to aap ney hum mein sey eik ko apni daeyn aur doosrey ko baain taraf khada kar liya aur unhoney baghair Azan aur iqaamat key namaz padhaai aur jab rukoo kartey they to apney haathon ki ungliyon ko eik dusrey mein phansa kar ghutnon key darmiyan rakh letey they. phir farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey huye dekha hai.
721,"Hazrat Aa'mash ki ye hadees Hazrat Is-haq bin Ibrahim ney hamein ba-waasta Nazr, Shoba sey mazkura hadees key hum maana bayan ki hai."
722,Hazrat Ibaad bin Tameem key chacha Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko masjid mein sidhey (chit) letey huye dekha. aap ney apna eik paaun doosrey paaun key ooper rakha huwa tha.
723,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke wo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein Masjide-Nabwi mein so jaya kartey they jab ke wo nojawan aur ghair shaadi shuda they aur unka ghar baar na tha.
724,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : masjid mein thooknaa ghalati (gunah) hai aur us ka kaffara ye hai ke usey dafn kar diya jaaey."
725,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu Anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qibley wali deewar par thook laga dekha. aap ney usey khurch diya, phir aap logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs namaz padhta ho to wo apney samney na thookey kyonkey jab insan namaz padhta hai to Allah uskey samney hota hai."
726,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney masjid ki qibley wali deewar par thook laga dekha. aap ney usey kankari sey khurch diya aur mana farmaya ke namazi apney samney ya daeyn thookey balke farmaya : wo apney baain janib thookey ya baain qadam key nichey.
727,"Hazrat Taariq bin Abdullah Muhaaribi (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to namaz padhta ho to apney samney ya daeyn janib na thook. agar khaali jagah ho (namazi na hon) to apney peechhey ya baain taraf thook warna aisey kar. aur aap ney paaun key nichey thookaa aur usey mil diya."
728,"Hazrat Shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap ney khankhaar phenka aur baain paaun sey mitti mein mal diya."
729,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney masjid ki samney wali deewar par khankhaar laga dekha to aap ghussey mein aagey yahan tak ke aap ka chehra anwar surkh ho gaya. ansaar ki eik aurat uthi us ney khankhaar ko khurchaa aur uski jagah khushbu laga di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye kya hi khub hai !
730,"Hazrat Abu-Humaid aur Hazrat Abu-Usaid Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi masjid mein dakhil ho to kahe : (اللھم ! افتح لی أبواب رحمتک), ''aey Allah ! merey liye apni rehmat key darwazey khol dey.'' aur jab masjid sey bahar nikley to kahey : (اللھم ! إنی اسالک من فضلک),''aey Allah ! main tujh sey tera Fazal maangta hun.''"
731,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi masjid mein dakhil ho to usey bethney sey pehley do rakatein padhni chaahiye."
732,"Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney apna waqiyaa bayan kartey huye farmaya, jab wo ghazwae-Tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey peechhey reh gaey they, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah key waqt tashrif laye, aur aap jab safar sey wapis aatey they to sab sey pehley masjid mein aatey aur do rakatein padhtey phir logon sey milney key liye beth jatey. (us din bhi) jab aap ney ye kuchh kar liya to jo log is ghazwey sey peechhey reh gaey they aa kar apna apna uzr pesh karney lagey aur (yaqeen dilaney key liye) qasmein khaney lagey. ye usi sey zayed aadmi they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey zahiri uzr ko qubul farmaya aur un sey baiate itaat ley li aur unkey liye bakhshish talab farmaee aur un ki batni (andar ki) haqiqat ko Allah Taala key supurd farma diya yahan tak ke main bhi aaya. jab mainey salam kaha to aap naraz shakhs ki tarah muskuraaey phir farmaya : aagey aa'o. main aa kar aap key samney beth gaya. aap ney puchha : tum kaisey peechey rahey? kya tum ney sawari nahin khareedi thi? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! agar main (aap ki bajaey) kisi duniya-daar (sardar) key paas betha hota to main janta hun ke yaqinan main uski narazi aur ghussey sey nikal jata kyonkey mujhey baat karney ka tariqa (khoob) inayat huwa hai. lekin Allah ki qism ! mujhey yaqin hai ke aap ko razi karney key liye agar mainey aap sey jhoot keh diya to Allah Taala aap ko mujh sey naraz kar deyga aur agar mainey aap ko sach sach keh diya to aap (waqti taur par) mujh sey naraz ho jaeyngey lekin mujhey ummid hai ke Allah Taala maaf farma deyga Allah ki qism ! main kabhi bhi is qadr sahibe-istataat aur sahulat nahin huwa jis qadr ab tha jab aap sey peechhey raha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is ney sach kaha hai (phir mujh sey farmaya : ) tum uth jao, yahan tak ke tumharey barey mein Allah Taala koi faisla farmaey. main uth key chala aaya. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
733,Hazrat Abu-Saeed bin Muallaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein bazar ko jatey huye masjid key paas sey guzartey to is mein namaz padhtey.
734,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq farishtey us shakhs key liye duayen kartey rehtey hain jo us jagah betha rehta hai jis jagah us ney namaz padhi : aey Allah ! isey maaf farma, aey Allah ! is par reham farma, jab tak wo be-wuzu na ho."
735,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs masjid mein beth kar agli namaz ka intizar karta hai, wo (hukman aur sawab key lihaz sey) namaz hi mein hota hai."
736,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney oonton key baadon mein namaz padhney sey mana farmaya hai.
737,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sari zamin merey liye sajda gaah aur tahaarat ka zariya banaee gaee hai, lihaza merey kisi ummati ko jahan bhi namaz ka waqt ho jaey, wo wahin namaz padh ley."
738,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey guzarish ki ke hamarey ghar tashrif laaeyn aur namaz padhein taake hum us jagah ko namaz key liye muqarrar kar len. aap tashrif laye to unhon (Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha)) ney eik chataai uthai aur usey pani sey geelaa kiya, phir aap ney namaz padhi aur sab (ghar walon) ney aap key peechhey namaz padhi."
739,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) chataai par namaz padh liya kartey they.
740,"Hazrat Abu-Haazim bin Dinar sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke kuchh aadmi Hazrat Sahal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye. darasal unka ikhtilaf ho gaya tha ke member kis lakdi sey bana tha? to unhoney un sey is barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main khub janta hun ke Membere-Nabawi kis lakdi sey bana tha. mainey isey usi din dekha tha jis din wo pehli martaba rakha gaya tha aur jab pehli dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) is par bethey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney falan aurat ko jis ka Sahal ney naam liya tha, pegham bheja : apney badhai ghulam sey keh ke wo merey liye member tayyar karey taake main jab logon sey baat cheet karun to is par betha karun. us aurat ney ghulam ko hukm diya to usney maqame-ghaaba key jhaaun key darkht sey member tayyar kiya, phir isey wo ley kar (us aurat key paas) aaya to us aurat ney isey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bhej diya. aap ney hukm diya to usey is jagah rakh diya gaya, phir mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap is par chadhey aur namaz shuru ki, aap ney member hi par takbire-tahreema kahi member hi par rukoo kiya, phir pichhley paaun nichey utrey aur member hi sey muttasil ho (lag) kar sajda kiya, phir dobara member par chadh gaey. jab farigh huye to logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : aey logo ! mainey ye is liye kiya hai taake tum meri iqtida (pairvi) kar sako aur meri namaz (ka tareeqa) seekh lo."
741,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko gadhey par sawar namaz padhtey dekha, jab ke aap khaibar ki taraf ja rahey they."
742,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko gadhey par sawar namaz padhtey dekha. aap khaibar ki taraf ja rahey they jab ke qibla aap ki pusht ki janib tha. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hum nahin jantey ke kisi aur raawi ney (Yasli Ali Himaar) key alfaz bayan karney mein Amr bin Yahya ki muwaafiqat ki ho. sahih baat ye hai ke Yahya bin Saeed ki Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey is mafhoom ki riwayat mauqoof hai. (واللہ أعلم)."
